Package Mathalg

Class Matrix<E extends Number>

java.lang.Object
Mathalg.Matrix<E>
public class Matrix<E extends Number> extends Object
This class contains various methods for manipulating with list <list<E>> and set it logic.

The documentation for the methods contained in this class includes brief descriptions of the implementations. Such descriptions should be regarded as implementation notes, rather than parts of the specification.

This class is a member of the Mathalg Framework.

0.1
